163
00:10:37,595 --> 00:10:38,888
Junkfood?

164
00:10:39,930 --> 00:10:40,930
Ja.

165
00:10:42,099 --> 00:10:43,559
Und Trocknertücher...

166
00:10:44,935 --> 00:10:46,187
